notes: Extended C++ optimization with bbox3. Ran for 30 minutes (1800 sec timeout) with 100000 iterations and 200 restarts per N value using 26 threads. Process was killed by timeout before completion. Log shows essentially ZERO improvement - only N=99 showed 0.0001% improvement, N=88 and N=151 showed tiny improvements. The solution is at a VERY STRONG LOCAL OPTIMUM that cannot be escaped even with extended optimization.
